{"tid":89363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"渣馬跑手包唔跟佢安排個個時間領取得唔得","createTime":"2017-01-21T09:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T17:17:46.000Z","uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4630ac162f31d8e9a5c546b1cabf2954674117","tid":89363,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次參加<br />\n佢個包時間安排左我2月4日12:00 pm - 2:00 pm<br />\n咁佢個開放時間係<br />\n2017年2月4及5日<br />\n上午9時30分至晚上7時<br />\n因為個日想返下工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我同一日去但早過12點OR 遲過2點攞又得唔得?<br />\nbtw 還掂佢都寄左封信黎 點解唔順手寄埋個包黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.    為確保領取跑手包期間人流暢順和減少等候時間，請各參賽者依照「跑手包領取書」所列出之指定日期及時間前往領取號碼布、計時晶片及跑手包。<br />\nSORRY 懶得打電話去問 所以上黎呢到問<br />\nTHANKS A LOT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e03ae8ed1f7f30740d4f10ed77ac3658f810d5","tid":89363,"uid":9489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"懶得打電話又打咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3325e086f842eb9a1d879a4454a00b3741211842","tid":89363,"uid":47478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:19:34.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢安排我10點去拎，一早仲要過海真係冇咩心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4cf1e72eda7a33534fe48474d6449c8f01dbabf","tid":89363,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懶得打電話又打咁多字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實有幾行係copy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電腦開post 都唔係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"